'''''Vedomosti''''' ({{lang-rus|Ведомости|p=ˈvʲedəməsʲtʲɪ}}, {{literally}} "The Record") is a [[Russian language|Russian-language]] [[business journalism|business]] [[daily newspaper|daily]] published in [[Moscow]].<ref>{{cite journal|author=Katja Koikkalainen|date=December 2007|title=The Local and the International in Russian Business Journalism: Structures and Practices|journal=Europe-Asia Studies|volume=59|issue=8|jstor=20451455}}</ref> It was previously a joint venture between [[Dow Jones and Company|Dow Jones]], the ''[[Financial Times]]''<ref>{{cite book|editor=Robert G. Picard|title=Media Firms: Structures, Operations, and Performance|date=2002|publisher=Lawrence Erlbaum Associates|location=Mahwah, NJ|page=61|url=https://www.questia.com/read/104790656/media-firms-structures-operations-and-performance|accessdate=26 December 2014}}{{Subscription required|via=Questia}}</ref> and the publishers of ''[[The Moscow Times]].''<ref name="Whalen1999">{{cite news|last1=Whalen|first1=Jeanne|title=Dow Jones, Pearson, Dutch PublisherJointly Launch Newspaper in Russia|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB936735778658629117|accessdate=29 September 2016|work=Wall Street Journal|date=8 September 1999}}</ref> The ''Financial Times'' and the ''Wall Street Journal'' sold their stakes in 2015, ahead of a new Russian media ownership law prohibiting foreign enterprises from owning more than 20% of stake in Russian media companies<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://rusplt.ru/news/bloomberg-druzya-putina-mogut-kupit-gazetu-vedomosti-220071.html|title=Bloomberg: друзья Путина готовятся купить газету «Ведомости»|access-date=2018-09-08}}</ref> which came into effect in 2016. [[Sanoma]] also sold its stake in the paper in 2015. The paper is now owned by Demyan Kudryavtsev, who also owns ''[[The Moscow Times]]'', and was previously chief executive of ''[[Kommersant]]''.<ref name="Sweney2015">{{cite news|last1=Sweney|first1=Mark|title=Pearson and Dow Jones sell stakes in Russian newspaper Vedomosti|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2015/nov/20/pearson-and-dow-jones-sell-stakes-in-russian-newspaper-vedomosti|accessdate=29 September 2016|work=The Guardian|date=20 November 2015}}</ref>

